00:57:20,991 --> 00:57:23,826
- Did you see the man upstairs, Sandra?
- A little.

590
00:57:24,036 --> 00:57:26,159
- Did you talk to him?
- No.

591
00:57:26,371 --> 00:57:28,280
Well, who did, Sandra?
Who talked to the man?

592
00:57:28,498 --> 00:57:30,242
Mary.

593
00:57:31,334 --> 00:57:32,745
Where is Mary, Sandra?

594
00:57:32,961 --> 00:57:34,455
