622
00:59:41,545 --> 00:59:44,166
You could always tell
when they were coming.

623
00:59:45,215 --> 00:59:47,421
Those songs.

624
00:59:48,635 --> 00:59:52,964
They'd charge through the snow.
Their guns froze.

625
00:59:53,974 --> 00:59:56,975
And that was OK
because we were better.

626
00:59:57,978 --> 01:00:00,350
Colder.

627
01:00:00,563 --> 01:00:04,182
At Chosin,
we were colder than anyone.

628
01:00:06,111 --> 01:00:08,103
Make it stop, Miss Henley!
Make it stop!

629
01:00:08,321 --> 01:00:12,235
- It’s OK. It’s OK.
- Make it stop! Make it stop!

630
01:00:12,450 --> 01:00:15,119
Shh.

631
01:00:15,328 --> 01:00:17,119
